item.dc:creator: elangovan7112002
item.content:encoded:
Projects

Welcome to my portfolio, where each project represents a testament to ingenuity, dedication, and excellence. Through a diverse array of endeavors, I've meticulously crafted prototypes and conducted impactful research, showcasing my versatility and innovation in tackling challenges. I look forward to the opportunity to collaborate and create impactful solutions together.

Face and Fingerprint Recognition

HTML forms the structure of the gym management website, while CSS is used to style the layout and appearance. JavaScript introduces interactivity,
such as dynamic membership listings and user management features. PHP handles the server-side logic, processing member requests, and interacting with the database. MySQL stores essential information such as membership details, user data, and payment records. The login/signup page, built using PHP and MySQL, authenticates users against the database, ensuring secure member registration.

Click Here

Dynamic Website

Developed Website for GTGraphix, integrating modern design and functionality to enhance user experience and effectively showcase client brands.

Click Here

Attendance Manger

Images are captured through the camera using OpenCV, and these images go through preprocessing steps such as resizing, filtering, and converting color spaces to improve data quality for further processing. For object detection, a cascade classifier is employed. The LBPH (Local Binary Patterns Histograms) algorithm examines the local texture patterns of the face and creates histograms of these patterns. These histograms are used to represent faces in the dataset, which are then stored in an Excel sheet.

Click Here

Portfolio

Key to the development of an website project, demonstrating proficiency in website design, front-end development, and it's my personal portfolio. fully created on wordpress                                             

Click Here

Food Order System

HTML structures the Food Ordering System (FOS), while CSS styles the layout and appearance. JavaScript introduces interactivity, such as dynamic food listings and user management features. The site includes an admin dashboard and a registration form. PHP handles server-side logic, processes user requests, and interacts with the database. MySQL stores essential information, including order details, user data, food categories, and menu items. The login/signup page, built using PHP and MySQL, authenticates users against the database, ensuring secure user registration.

Click Here

Chat Bot

Implemented a dynamic chatbot website project, offering personalized assistance and demonstrating proficiency in AI integration and user engagement strategies

Click Here

Let's get connected to Eachother

Please feel free to reach out at your convenience. I'm eager to discuss how our expertise aligns with your objectives and how we can work together to achieve mutual success

item.title: Contact
item.dc:creator: elangovan7112002
item.content:encoded:
If you're looking for a skilled freelancer to bring your web development projects to life? Look no further! With expertise in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, WordPress, Python, and proficiency in Figma, PHP, and MySQL, I am well-equipped to handle a wide range of tasks.

Whether you need assistance with website design, front-end development, WordPress customization, or backend programming, I have the knowledge and experience to deliver high-quality results. Additionally, my proficiency in Figma allows for seamless collaboration on design projects, ensuring a cohesive and polished final product.

Furthermore, I bring a solid foundation in PHP and MySQL, enabling me to create dynamic and functional web applications tailored to your specific requirements.

Whether you have a short-term project or a long-term employment opportunity, I am ready to contribute my expertise and drive your projects to success.

Fill out the form below to discuss your needs further. I'll get back to you as soon as possible.

Thank you for considering me. I look forward to the opportunity to work with you.

ContactPlease enable JavaScript in your browser to complete this form.
